Team 254 is excited to share the code for our 2022 robot: Sideways. If you have any questions, feel free to ask!

GitHub

GitHub - Team254/FRC-2022-Public

Contribute to Team254/FRC-2022-Public development by creating an account on GitHub.

Some highlights of our 2022 codebase include:

  • Field-Centric Swerve Drive
  • Superstructure with Two-Sided Intake, Automatic Wrong Ball Rejection, Super Eject, Automatic Turret Tracking
  • Shooting on the Move
  • Feedforward + Proportional Feedback Controller for Autonomous Path Following
  • Fully Automated Climb
